# Automate acceptance & integration

## Điều kiện

- Bước **3 Formulate**: `.feature` R3 (+ mirror R4).
- Bước **4**: unit domain **xanh**.

## Layers (Screenplay — UI `@ui`)

```text
Gherkin step → step-definitions → tasks → questions → page objects (tests/ui/pages/)
```

## Map theo tag

| Tag | Pattern | Path |
|-----|---------|------|
| `@api` / domain | Step → domain/use case | `tests/step-definitions/fn##/` |
| `@ui` | Screenplay + Playwright | `tests/ui/`, `tests/features/fn##/*_ui.feature` |
| `@perf` | k6 + Gherkin gate | `tests/perf/k6/`, `@perf` (`14-performance-bdd.mdc`) |
| `@smoke` / `@regression` | Subset CI | filter tag Cucumber |

## UI (Expo Web)

- `testID` → `data-testid`; deep link `/?e2e=1&screen=…`
- `npm run test:bdd:ui`

## Integration

- `tests/integration/` — adapter thật (DB/API mock/staging).

## Đầu ra

Acceptance ổn định trên môi trường test → tick **Task 5** dev plan.
